parameters: \n<Adam>Put that back, have some respect for the dead!
\n<Sabrina>Fine, but you're buying me a similar outfit.
\n<Adam>I'm guess you also already have figured out this is a trap.
\n<Sabrina>A giant crystal thing in the middle of an ancient room. How do you not
expect giant boulders, snake pits, and so on not to come kill us?
\n<Adam>Might as well get it over with.
